concepts used : 
   1. Tree
   2. recursion

code :

class Solution {
    public boolean solve (TreeNode root){
        if(root.left == null && root.right == null ){  
            if(root.val == 1){
                return true;
            }
            return false;
        }

        boolean left = solve(root.left);
        boolean right = solve(root.right);
        if(root.val == 2){
            return left || right;
        }
        return left && right;
    }
    public boolean evaluateTree(TreeNode root) {
        if(root.left == null && root.right == null ){  
            if(root.val == 1){
                return true;
            }
            return false;
        }
        return solve(root);
        
        
    }
}

Time complexity = O(n)
space complexity = O(1)
